
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Error Page | CineVibes</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e50914, #000);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .full-height-container {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .alert-box {
      background-color: #1c1c1c;
      border: 1px solid #ff4c4c;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 76, 76, 0.5);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    footer {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e0702, #4f2402);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      color: white;
    }
    .alert-box h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #ff4c4c;
    }

    .alert-box p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-custom {
      background-color: #ff4c4c;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn-custom:hover {
      background-color: #cc0000;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .alert-box h1 {
        font-size: 1.7rem;
      }

      .alert-box p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .btn-custom {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="full-height-container">
    <div class="alert-box">
      <h1>ðŸš« Oops! Something went wrong</h1>
      <p>The page you're trying to reach is broken or doesn't exist.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-custom">Go Back Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer style="margin-top: 50px;">
    <p>&copy; 2025 CineVibes. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
